'''永寧陵'''（後來認為是「蕭統墓」）位于[[江苏省|江苏省]][[南京市|南京市]][[栖霞街道|栖霞街道]]甘家巷獅子沖，原被當成是[[中国|中国]][[南北朝|南北朝]]时[[陈朝|陈朝]][[陈文帝|文帝陈蒨]]的陵墓<ref>The Book of Chen and the History of Southern Dynasties recorded that Chen Bozong was born in 554 and that he was older than Chen Bomao, but inconsistently gave Chen Bomao's age at death to be 17, which would make him born in 551, three years before Chen Bozong's birth. As Chen Bozong and Chen Bomao had the same mother -- Empress Shen -- it would appear that 555 is a more likely date, although there are obvious problems with Chen Bozong's own birthdate -- with regard to which, see Emperor Fei of Chen</ref>。不過，据後來的出土资料（砖面刻划「[[中大通|中大通]]弍年」、「[[普通|普通]]七年」），这两座大墓的墓主人推断為梁昭明太子[[蕭統|蕭統]]及其生母丁贵嫔，而非陈文帝。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=南京市考古研究所 |title=南京栖霞狮子冲南朝大墓发掘简报 |url=http://dnwh.njmuseum.com/pdf/2015/201504/20150405.pdf |journal= |access-date=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2020-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722171215/http://dnwh.njmuseum.com/pdf/2015/201504/20150405.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=南朝大墓墓主身份重新確認昭明太子蕭統：隕落的「學術男神」 |url=https://www.zz-news.com/com/gjrwls/news/itemid-852290.html}}</ref>

墓已平。现存石[[天禄|天禄]]、[[麒麟|麒麟]]各一。二者分距东西，相距26米，天禄已残，麒麟长3.1米，胸宽1.45米，高2.85米。
